Text:
Thanks for UL.  However after unzipping i'm still left with 'Launch WinRAR.exe' and 'WinRAR.exe' which still seem to be zipped and double clicking brings up the unzipper.  What should i do at this point?  
Thanks

@jg4545
This one is supposed to be used on systems where you don't have already installed WinRAR, even if it doesn't makes any harm to it. Running the program on a clean machine you 'll get the WR functions in the menu when you click with the right mousebutton on a file. Obviously if you already have WinRAR installed you 'll not see any difference.
